name: Good Deed Robos by Flow Klein

metadata.name: Good Deed Robo #2
metadata.description:
The "Good Deed Robos" each performed one good deed that you own through this NFT! Your NFT is your certificate of ownership of this good deed.

In addition your Robo will be your loving companion! It reminds you and everyone else that even small good deeds make the world a better place. And you helped achieving that!

Owning a "Good Deed Robo" means you brightened someones day, helped someone in need or simply that you did something good.
